0spent%20much%20of%20his%20time%20inside%20Dhaka's%20courtrooms%2C%20fighting%20about%20200%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20his%20associates%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20graft.%20He%20and%20his%20supporters%20say%20Hasina's%20government%20was%20behind%20the%20legal%20pressure%20and%20perhaps%20saw%20him%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20her%20power.%20She%20denied%20those%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%2084%2C%20is%20best%20known%20for%20founding%20Grameen%20Bank%20and%20pioneering%20microcredit%20-%20providing%20tiny%20business%20loans%20to%20the%20world's%20poorest%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women.%20Though%20he's%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20life%20in%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20politics%20is%20largely%20unexplored%20terrain.%20In%202007%2C%20the%20Bangladeshi%20government%20splintered%2C%20and%20the%20military%20seized%20power.%20Yunus%2C%20who'd%20never%20run%20for%20office%2C%20considered%20forming%20a%20new%20party%20to%20fill%20the%20vacuum%2C%20but%20ultimately%20scrapped%20the%20idea%20within%20a%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20uncomfortable%20with%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20brings%20star%20power%20to%20the%20role%20and%20is%20a%20popular%20choice%20with%20many%20Western%20governments.%20His%20supporters%20span%20industries%20and%20continents.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he's%20cultivated%20friendships%20with%20European%20royals%2C%20business%20titans%20like%20Richard%20Branson%20and%20the%20Clintons%2C%20who%20helped%20Yunus%20expand%20his%20microcredit%20initiatives%20to%20the%20US.%20His%20friends%20say%20he's%20a%20rare%20visionary%20with%20a%20genuine%20commitment%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20uplifting%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Polman%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20executive%20of%20Unilever%20Plc%20and%20a%20close%20friend.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20moral%20leader.%20He's%20not%20somebody%20who%20likes%20to%20talk%20about%20himself.%20He%20likes%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20people%20he%20serves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20reputation%20has%20endeared%20him%20to%20many%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20including%20the%20military%2C%20which%20had%20previously%20supported%20his%20first%20foray%20into%20politics.%20After%20winning%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20in%202006%2C%20thousands%20of%20Bangladeshis%20crowded%20venues%20just%20to%20hear%20him%20speak.%20Many%20still%20bow%20and%20touch%20their%20hearts%20when%20they%20see%20him.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Yunus%20has%20focused%20on%20expanding%20dozens%20of%20social%20businesses%2C%20including%20ones%20that%20offer%20free%20health%20care%2C%20vocational%20training%20and%20phone%20services%20to%20poorer%20Bangladeshis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Muhammad%20Yunus%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Dhaka.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Muhammad%20Yunus%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Dhaka.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F4dhpif0g_muhammad-yunus-bloomberg_625x300_07_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20Yunus%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Dhaka.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20Yunus%20pivots%20more%20deliberately%20into%20politics%20-%20or%20simply%20fills%20a%20hole%20before%20elections%20are%20held%20-%20remains%20unclear.%20As%20protesters%20swarmed%20Dhaka's%20streets%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Yunus%20spoke%20out%20publicly%20against%20the%20violence%20and%20characterized%20Hasina's%20crackdown%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20-%20but%20he%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20ambitions%20to%20take%20a%20more%20formal%20role%20in%20shaping%20a%20new%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20politician%2C%26