%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243ae7d96-1eb5-4644-9a83-7afc8f0ef4d9%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20why%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHow%2C%20now%2041%2C%20said%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-early-financial-independence-mindful-spending-investing-berlin-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20motivation%20to%20retire%20early%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20his%20identity%20tied%20to%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20job%20is%20not%20everything%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20how%20early%20I%20could%20get%20out%20of%20the%20rat%20race%20that%20made%20me%20want%20to%20try%20this%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20starting%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Independence%20Retire%20Early%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-retiring-early-fire-movement-financial-independence-millionaire-savings-work-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20said%20he%20came%20from%20a%20humble%20Singaporean%20family%20and%20grew%20up%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20financial%20hardship%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTowards%20my%20final%20year%20of%20my%20diploma%2C%20I%20stopped%20taking%20pocket%20money.%20Even%20the%20remainder%20of%20my%20course%20fees%20was%20on%20my%20own%2C%20just%20taking%20up%20part-time%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20learning%20the%20importance%20of%20at%20least%20saving%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20motivation%20has%20mostly%20been%20for%20the%20money%20than%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20his%20reason%20for%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c98be9e-0fa8-4b1b-8f58-210100969796%5C%