5C%22%3EKlarna%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20an%20AI%20assistant%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt5-gpt4-expectations-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E's%20models%20was%20doing%20the%20equivalent%20work%20of%20700%20full-time%20customer-service%20agents.%20Last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharma-cio-cancelled-microsoft-copilot-ai-tool-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20cited%20what's%20happening%20in%20contact%20centers%20with%20its%20Dynamics%20software%20as%20an%20example%20AI%20being%20deployed%20successfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20no%20one%20really%20wants%20their%20customer-service%20questions%20handled%20by%20machines.%20Not%20even%20the%20young'uns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20research%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20which%20has%20been%20closely%20tracking%20AI%20adoption%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d734e6a8-86c5-4fec-9f0c-1b9d8cabec7a%5C%22%3EAsk%20the%20interns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20bank%20surveys%20its%20interns%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20to%20get%20a%20gut-check%20on%20tech%20usage%20from%20younger%20people%20who%20will%20grow%20into%20tomorrow's%20big%20consumers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20recently%20asked%20these%20interns%20about%20using%20AI-powered%20customer-service%20agents.%20The%20results%20were%20not%20pretty.%20It's%20another%20warning%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%20about%20the%20potential%20limits%20of%20AI%20adoption%20in%20practical%20situations.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20majority%20(93%25)%20prefer%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20human%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20solving%20a%20query%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E10%25%20said%20AI%20chatbots%20never%20solve%20their%20problems%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E75%25%20said%20chatbots%20fail%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20time%20to%20solve%20their%20problem%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221990%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20from%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20research%20note%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b27fe2b4912df3ae195629%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221299%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chart%20from%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20research%20note%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%20analysts%20noted%20that%20AI%20models%20should%20improve%2C%20helping%20machines%20to%20solve%20more%20customer-service%20questions%20and%20complaints.%20But%20they%20also%20highlighted%20another%20risk.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20cases%20technology%20improvement%20in%20and%20of%20itself%20cannot%20force%20behavioural%20change%20that%20is%20generally%20slow%20and%20iterative%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20emotionally-driven%20complaints%20or%20trust-centric%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20this%20week%20to%20investors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20sense%20intuitively.%20When%20you%20have%20problem%2C%20especially%20one%20involving%20something%20you%20paid%20real%20money%20for%2C%20you%20want%20to%20be%20heard%20by%20a%20human%20who%20feels%20your%20pain%20and%20is%20capable%20of%20fixing%20the%20issue%20asap%2C%20ideally%20by%20cutting%20through%20red%20tape%20and%20just%20getting%20it%20done.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229acd33e1-b0e5-4a29-837b-543b15233289%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20reality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20reality%20is%20nowhere%20near%20that%20at%20the%20moment.%20Take%20Klarna's%20AI%20customer-service%20agents.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoftware%20engineer%20Gergely%20Orosz%20tried%20this%20Klarna%20technology%20out%20by%20calling%20up%20with%20questions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUnderwhelming%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20conclusion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20asked%20about%20something%2C%20the%20AI%20bo