to%20be%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20bear%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECredit%20markets%20remain%20stable%2C%20and%20only%20three%20of%2010%20signals%20of%20a%20market%20peak%20have%20flashed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20of%20our%20sentiment%20signals%20suggest%20that%20sentiment%20did%20not%20hit%20euphoric%20levels%20typically%20seen%20at%20the%20end%20of%20bull%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20BofA%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20market's%20recent%20sharp%20sell-off%20is%20unlikely%20to%20transform%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20bear%20market%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-picks-up-recession-fears-carry-trade-unwind-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%20fell%20as%20much%20as%208%25%20since%20its%20record%20high%20in%20July%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20plunged%20more%20than%2010%25.%20The%20sell-off%20was%20driven%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsahm-rule-recession-outlook-indicator-triggered-unemployment-rate-jobs-report-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20weak%20July%20jobs%20report%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20unwind%20of%20the%20yen%20carry%20trade%2C%20and%20concerns%20of%20an%20imminent%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbac-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategist%20Savita%20Subramanian%2C%20the%20tell-tale%20signs%20of%20a%20stock%20market%20peak%20have%20yet%20to%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20this%20being%20a%20stock%20market%20peak%20that's%20on%20the%20precipice%20of%20a%20massive%20drawdown%2C%20it's%20more%20than%20likely%20just%20a%20typical%20correction%20that%20occurs%20on%20average%20every%20single%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20perspective%2C%20Subramanian%20pointed%20to%20stock%20market%20history%20to%20highlight%20that%20pullbacks%20in%20the%20market%20are%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B5%25%2B%20pullbacks%20are%20common%2C%20occurring%20over%20three%20times%20per%20year%20on%20average%20since%201930%20(this%20marks%20the%20second%20one%20this%20year%20after%20April).%20Larger%20corrections%20are%20less%20frequent%20but%20still%20common%2C%20with%2010%25%2B%20corrections%20occurring%20once%20per%20year%20on%20average%20(the%20last%20one%20was%20in%20fall%202023)%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20credit%20markets%20remain%20stable%20gives%20Subramanian%20confidence%20that%20the%20recent%20sell-off%20is%20a%20common%20pullback%20rather%20than%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20true%20bear%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20credit%20markets%20are%20subdued%20with%20a%20trough-to-peak%20widening%20of%2070bp%20for%20high-yield%20spreads%20through%20last%20Friday%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%20during%20panics%20that%20evolve%20into%20bear%20markets%2C%20bond%20investors%20demand%20a%20higher%20premium%20for%20their%20risky%20junk%20debt%20relative%20to%20Treasurys%2C%20but%20that%20has%20yet%20to%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BofA%20US%20High%20Yield%20option%20adjusted%20spread%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20difference%20in%20yields%20between%20junk%20bonds%20and%20Treasury%20bonds%2C%20is%20at%20just%203.93%25%2C%20well%20below%20its%205.33%25%20average%20since%20inception%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20perspective%2C%20prior%20stock%20market%20panics%20in%202020%20and%202008%20led%20the%20spread%20to%20soar%20to%209.82%25%20and%2021.82%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20spread%20widening%20can%20be%20described%20as%20normalization%20from%20extremely%20tight%20levels%20toward%20fair%20value.%20Spread%20widening%20beyond%20450-475%20would%20be%20concerning%2C%20according%20to%20our%20credit%20strategists%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20Subramanian%20tracks%2010%20signals%20that%2C%20when%20most%20of%20them%20flash%2C%20signals%20that%20a%20major%20stock%20market%20peak%20has%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20of%20July%2C%20just%20three%20of%20the%2010%20signals%20have%20flashed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note%2C%20which%20was%20a%20stepdown%20from%20the%205%20signals%20that%20flashed%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221305%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20market%20peak%20signals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b26b6ea5247369a3e9df82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20a%20maximum%20of%2050%25%20of%20these%20signals%20triggered%20in%20June%2C%20below%20the%20average%20of%2070%25%20triggered%20in%20prior%20market%20peaks%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20stock%20market%20peak%20signals%20that%20flashed%20in%20July%20include%20the%20net%20percentage%20of%20respondents%20to%20the%20Conference%20Board%20survey%20exceeding%2020%20when%20asked%20if%20they%20expect%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20keep%20rising%2C%20an%20inverted%20yield%20curve%2C%20and%20tightening%20credit%20conditions%20based%20on%20the%20Senior%20Loan%20Officer%20Opinion%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20seven%20other%20signals%20tied%20to%20investor%20sentiment%2C%20valuations%2C%20and%20macro%20data%20have%20yet%20to%20flash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20of%20our%20sentiment%20signals%2C%20including%20our%20Sell%20Side%20Indicator%2C%20suggest%20that%20sentiment%20did%20not%20hit%20euphoric%20levels%20typically%20seen%20at%20the%20end%20of%20bull%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20preparing%20for%20a%20prolonged%20market%20sell-off%2C%20Subramanian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbuy-defensive-stocks-to-weather-historic-stock-market-volatility-bofa-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecommends%20investors%20go%20bargain%20hunting%20and%20focus%20on%20buying%20high%20quality%20stocks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-bear-decline-unlikely-only-3-signals-flash-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722972033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b267a2a5247369a3e9dbb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-bear-decline-unlikely-only-3-signals-flash-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSeveral%20of%20our%20sentiment%20signals%20suggest%20that%20sentiment%20did%20not%20hit%20euphoric%20levels%20typically%20seen%20at%20the%20end%20of%20bull%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20BofA%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A177%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-bear-decline-unlikely-only-3-signals-flash-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Tech%20reform%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20courts%2C%20not%20Congress.%20Is%20that%20good%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20testifies%20in%20Congress%20in%202018%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b272d1a5247369a3e9e3bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223347%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20has%20been%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20defending%20Google%20to%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Big%20Tech%20regulation%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20courts.%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20government%20won%20a%20major%20Big%20Tech%20antitrust%20battle%20this%20week%2C%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWashington%20has%20several%20more%20legal%20fights%20brewing%20against%20other%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it's%20notable%20that%20all%20the%20tech-reform%20talk%20you%20used%20to%20hear%20from%20Congress%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20has%20just%20gone%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20ruling%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-violated-antitrust-law-to-keep-search-monopoly-judge-rules-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20is%20an%20illegal%20monopolist%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20major%20victory%20for%20the%20yearslong%20movement%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20giant%20tech%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20victories%20that%20movement%20has%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20tellingly%2C%20it%20didn't%20come%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20new%20law%2C%20but%20from%20a%20judge's%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20in%20the%20US%2C%20that's%20how%20we're%20doing%20things%20these%20days%3A%20Congress%20can't%20or%20won't%20act.%20So%20people%20who%20want%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20to%20change%20their%20ways%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20it%20via%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20very%20brief%20history%20lesson%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCommunications_Decency_Act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20piece%20of%20meaningful%20legislation%20that%20regulated%20tech%20is%20from%201996%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20the%20internet%20was%20a%20novelty.%20Since%20then%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20has%20grown%20pretty%20much%20unchecked%2C%20and%20despite%20some%20murmurs%20that%20maybe%20someone%20should%20do%20%E2%80%A6%20%3Cem%3Esomething%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20power%20the%20biggest%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20have%20accumulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20Donald%20Trump's%202016%20election%2C%20those%20concerns%20turned%20into%20a%20full-blown%20movement%2C%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20lawmakers%20promising%20real%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20then%20%E2%80%A6%20very%20little%20has%20happened.%20With%20two%20exceptions%20%E2%80%94%20the%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFOSTA-SESTA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFOSTA%20and%20SESTA%3C%2Fa%3E%20acts%2C%20aimed%20at%20sex%20trafficking%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-passes-house-bytedance-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20year's%20bill%20forcing%20TikTok%20to%20find%20a%20US%20owner%20or%20leave%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Congress%20hasn't%20passed%20any%20laws%20that%20would%20meaningfully%20restrain%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Ftechnology%2F3900219-david-cicilline-led-the-fight-against-big-tech-heres-what-comes-next%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20debate%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20happened%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Partisan%20gridlock%3F%20Well-funded%20pushback%20from%20the%20targeted%20companies%3F%20The%20fact%20that%20most%20Americans%20really%20like%20individual%20Big%20Tech%20companies%3F%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20result%20is%20still%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20any%20real%20reform%20we%20see%20in%20Big%20Tech%20will%20come%20from%20a%20courtroom%20via%20challenges%20launched%20by%20the%20federal%20government.%20This%20week's%20Google%20ruling%20came%20out%20of%20a%20lawsuit%20first%20filed%20by%20Trump's%20Department%20of%20Justice%3B%20the%20Trump-era%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20also%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20has%20brought%20charges%20against%20Amazon%20and%20Apple%2C%20along%20with%20a%20separate%20case%20against%20Google.%20It%20also%20refiled%20the%20Trump-era%20Meta%20case%20after%20a%20court%20turned%20the%20first%20attempt%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Biden's%20administration%20has%20used%20the%20courts%20in%20another%20way%2C%20too%3A%20It%20has%20either%20sued%20or%20threatened%20to%20sue%20to%20stop%20a%20whole%20series%20of%20Big%20Tech%20acquisitions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnymag.com%2Fintelligencer%2F2023%2F12%2Flina-khans-rough-year-running-the-federal-trade-commission.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20track%20record%20for%20the%20suits%20it%20has%20brought%20hasn't%20been%20very%20good%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20threat%20of%20litigation%20has%2C%20at%20a%20minimum%2C%20slowed%20down%20Big%20Tech%20M%26amp%3BA%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20any%20of%20that%20mean%20anything%2C%20long%20term%3F%20We%20have%20no%20idea.%20The%20lawsuits%20in%20progress%20could%20take%20years%20to%20resolve.%20Appeals%20like%20the%20one%20the%20company%20promises%20to%20bring%20against%20this%20week's%20decision%20will%20extend%20the%20timeline%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20remembering%20that%20the%20last%20time%20the%20government%20used%20the%20courts%20to%20try%20to%20curtail%20Big%20Tech%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FUnited_States_v._Microsoft_Corp.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%201998%20when%20it%20went%20after%20Microsoft%20for%20monopolizing%20internet%20access%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20federal%20court%20declared%20that%20Microsoft%20should%20be%20broken%20up.%20But%20Microsoft%20successfully%20appealed%20that%20ruling%20and%20ended%20up%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.google.com%2Fscholar_case%3Fcase%3D14986020318509032386%26q%3D373%2BF.3d%2B1199%26hl%3Den%26as_sdt%3D6%2C39%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20settlement%20that%20ultimately%20took%20effect%20in%202004%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20may%20have%20noticed%20that%20Microsoft%20remains%20incredibly%20powerful%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flip%20side%3A%20At%20least%20some%20former%20Microsoft%20executives%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20government's%20legal%20case%20slowed%20the%20company%20down%20significantly%2C%20even%20if%20the%20company%20stayed%20intact.%20They%20argue%20that%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20and%20everything%20around%20them%20made%20Microsoft%20more%20timid%20and%20less%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20shifts%2C%20like%20the%20move%20from%20PCs%20to%20mobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20think%20Big%20Tech%20is%20So%20Big%20That%20Something%20Must%20Be%20Done%2C%20taking%20those%20companies%20to%20court%20is%20anything%20but%20a%20sure%20thing.%20But%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20only%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-antitrust-courts-not-congress-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722972005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b272f7393cd3c8629bb40f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-antitrust-courts-not-congress-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Politicians%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20about%20taking%20on%20Big%20Tech%20giants%20like%20Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai.%20Instead%2C%20they've%20outsourced%20the%20work%20to%20lawsuits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A84%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-antitrust-courts-not-congress-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tim%20Walz%20VP%20announcement%20sp