nes-says-kamala-harris-picked-tim-walz-over-josh-shapiro-because-%2Famp_articleshow%2F112326961.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvan-jones-says-kamala-harris-picked-tim-walz-over-josh-shapiro-because-%2Famp_articleshow%2F112326961.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sheikh%20Hasina%20Hasn't%20Sought%20Asylum%20Anywhere%2C%20Her%20Son%20Tells%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20in%20India%20for%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%20has%20not%20sought%20asylum%20%26quot%3Banywhere%26quot%3B%2C%20her%20son%20categorically%20told%20NDTV%20today%2C%20brushing%20off%20speculation.%20Ms%20Hasina%2C%2076%2C%20was%20contemplating%20retirement%20anyway%20and%20now%20she%20will%20retire%20from%20politics%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20divide%20her%20time%20between%20her%20family%20members%2C%20added%20Sajeeb%20Wazed%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Washington.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20multiple%20reports%20about%20UK's%20%26quot%3Bsilence%26quot%3B%20her%20request%20for%20asylum%20and%20revocation%20of%20her%20visa%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Mr%20Wazed%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20reports%20about%20her%20requesting%20asylum%20are%20incorrect.%20She%20has%20not%20requested%20asylum%20anywhere.%20So%20the%20question%20of%20UK%20or%20US%20not%20responding%20yet%20is%20not%20true%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20US%20Visa%20revocation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20no%20such%20discussion%20with%20the%20US%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wazed%2C%20who%20made%20headlines%20yesterday%20saying%20his%20mother%20will%20quit%20politics%2C%20reiterated%20it%20today.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20done%20with%20politics%20in%20Bangladesh...%20my%20mother%20was%20planning%20to%20retire%20anyway%2C%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20her%20last%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20now%20planning%20to%20spend%20time%20together%20-%20where%20and%20how%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20worked%20out.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20in%20Washington%2C%20my%20aunt%20is%20in%20London%2C%20my%20sister%20lives%20in%20Delhi%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20know%2C%20she%20might%20travel%20between%20the%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina's%20aircraft%20provided%20by%20the%20Bangladesh%20armed%20forces%20had%20landed%20at%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20base%20in%20Hindon%20near%20Delhi%20yesterday%2C%20shortly%20after%20taking%20off%20from%20Dhaka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20very%20short%20notice%2C%20she%20requested%20approval%20to%20come%20for%20the%20moment%20to%20India.%20We%20simultaneously%20received%20a%20request%20for%20flight%20clearance%20from%20the%20Bangladesh%20authorities.%20She%20arrived%20yesterday%20evening%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20government%20yet%20to%20announce%20how%20long%20she%20will%20be%20staying%2C%20there%20has%20been%20much%20speculation%20about%20her%20final%20destination.%20A%20number%20of%20names%20have%20come%20up%2C%20including%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20even%20Finland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20had%20described%20the%20situation%20in%20Dhaka%20as%20%26quot%3Bevolving%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Border%20Security%20Force%20is%20on%20high%20alert%20across%20India's%204%2C096-km%20border%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20are%20porous.%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20stopped%20trains%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20most%20carriers%20have%20cancelled%20flights%20to%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722967320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fe2gcqjlg_sheikh-hasina_625x300_06_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshe