0gains%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20sale%20of%20capital%20assets%20after%20adjusting%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20experts%20had%20said%20that%20the%20proposed%20changes%20in%20the%20Budget%20would%20raise%20the%20LTCG%20tax%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20amendments%20to%20Finance%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20circulated%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20individuals%20or%20HuF%20who%20bought%20houses%20before%20July%2023%2C%202024%2C%20can%20compute%20his%2Fher%20taxes%20under%20the%20new%20scheme%20%5B%4012.5%20per%20cent%20without%20indexation%5D%20and%20old%20scheme%20%5B%4020%20per%20cent%20with%20indexation%5D%20and%20pay%20such%20tax%20which%20is%20lower%20of%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Budget%20presentation%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20said%20that%20'substantial%20tax%20savings'%20are%20expected%20for%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20taxpayers%20due%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20long-term%20capital%20gains%20tax%20(LTCG)%20rate%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20changes%20brought%20in%20the%202024-25%20Budget%2C%20the%20government%20has%20retained%20the%20indexation%20benefit%20for%20taxpayers%20on%20properties%20bought%20or%20inherited%20before%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogesh%20Kale%2C%20Executive%20Director%2C%20Nangia%20Andersen%20India%20said%20through%20the%20amendments%20proposed%20to%20the%20new%20capital%20gain%20tax%20regime%20introduced%20in%20Budget%202024%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20tried%20to%20appease%20the%20taxpayers%20by%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20raised%20to%20some%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20abolishment%20of%20indexation%20benefit%20continues%2C%20properties%20acquired%20prior%20to%2023rd%20July%202024%20are%20proposed%20to%20be%20grandfathered%20with%20the%20option%20to%20the%20taxpayers%20to%20offer%20the%20capital%20gain%20tax%20either%20at%2012.5%25%20without%20indexation%20or%2020%25%20with%20indexation%2C%20whichever%20is%20more%20beneficial%2C%26quot%3B%20Kale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGouri%20Puri%2C%20Partner%2C%20Shardul%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20said%20This%20will%20quell%20taxpayer%20concerns%20around%20losing%20indexation%20benefits%20as%20a%20trade-off%20for%20a%20lower%20long-term%20capital%20gains%20tax%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaxpayers%20can%20choose%20the%20more%20beneficial%20regime%20and%20should%20not%20be%20worse%20off%20because%20of%20change%20in%20law.%20Concerns%20around%20taxation%20of%20inflationary%20gains%20in%20respect%20of%20immovable%20property%20acquired%20prior%20to%20a%20change%20in%20the%20law%20have%20been%20addressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Puri%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722966360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-11%2Freal-estate-generic-650_650x400_51447690539.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fcentre-to-ease-long-term-capital-gains-tax-for-sale-of-properties-in-budget-6278503%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20proposed%20a%20relief%20to%20taxpayers%20with%20respect%20to%20capital%20gain%20tax%20on%20real%20estate%20properties%20by%20giving%20them%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20between%2020%20per%20cent%20and%2012.5%20per%20cent%20tax%20rates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fcentre-to-ease-long-term-capital-gains-tax-for-sale-of-properties-in-budget-6278503%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fcentre-to-ease-long-term-capital-gains-tax-for-sale-of-properties-in-budget-6278503%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2