ut%20his%20wife's%20struggle%20to%20conceive%20and%20then%20opting%20for%20IVF%20to%20become%20parents.%20Tim%20and%20Gwen%20Walz%20have%20two%20children%20%3A%2023-year-old%20Hope%20and%2017-year-old%20Gus%20Walz.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-tim-walz-spoke-about-ivf-chidlless-cat-ladies%2Farticleshow%2F112326208.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-tim-walz-spoke-about-ivf-chidlless-cat-ladies%2Famp_articleshow%2F112326208.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhen-tim-walz-spoke-about-ivf-chidlless-cat-ladies%2Famp_articleshow%2F112326208.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2240%20Years%20On%2C%20Life%20Term%20Of%203%20Convicts%20In%20'Murder'%20Over%20Mangoes%20Cut%20To%207%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForty%20years%20after%20three%20men%20were%20booked%20for%20murder%20following%20a%20trivial%20fight%20among%20children%20over%20mangoes%20in%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20village%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20come%20to%20their%20rescue%20by%20reducing%20the%20life%20sentence%20to%20a%20seven-year%20jail%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentence%20has%20been%20awarded%20for%20a%20lesser%20offence%20of%20culpable%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201984%2C%20three%20men%20were%20booked%20for%20murder%20of%20a%20fellow%20villager%20by%20hitting%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3E'lathi'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stick)%20on%20the%20head.%20The%20trial%20court%20in%201986%20convicted%20them%20for%20murder%20and%20sentenced%20them%20for%20life%2C%20while%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202022%20confirmed%20the%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20them%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20in%20Gonda%20district%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20five%20convicts%20passed%20away%20during%20pendency%20of%20appeal%20before%20the%20high%20court%20and%20proceedings%20against%20them%20were%20abated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20and%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20said%20considering%20the%20totality%20of%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20case%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20injuries%20on%20the%20dead%20man%20and%20also%20considering%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20weapon%20used%20which%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3E'lathi'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20inclined%20to%20accept%20the%20argument%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20and%20it%20is%20not%20murder%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20from%20the%20deposition%20of%20all%20the%20eyewitnesses%20in%20the%20case%2C%20it%20has%20come%20on%20record%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20case%20of%20pre-planned%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20we%20convert%20the%20findings%20of%20section%20302%20(murder)%20of%20IPC%20to%20that%20of%20Section%20304%20Part-I%20of%20IPC%2C%20and%20thereby%20convert%20the%20sentence%20of%20life%20imprisonment%20of%20all%20the%20appellants%20before%20us%20to%20that%20of%20seven%20years%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20along%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20to%20be%20given%20by%20each%20appellant%20which%20shall%20be%20deposited%20by%20them%20within%20a%20period%20of%20eight%20weeks%20from%20today%2C%20if%20not%20already%20deposited%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20its%20order%20of%20July%2024%20but%20uploaded%20recently%20on%20the%20top%20court's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20to%20be%20deposited%20shall%20be%20given%20to%20the%20victim's%20family%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20and%20fastened%20the%20responsibility%20to%20the%20district%20magistrate%20of%20Gonda%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20compliance%20of%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20convicts%20Man%20Bahadur%20Singh%2C%20Bharat%20Singh%20and%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Singh%20through%20their%20lawyer%20Saksham%20Maheshwari%20have%20argued%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20murder%20but%20it%20is%20a%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20as%20it%20would%20come%20under%20Exception%204%20of%20Section%20300%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EException%204%20of%20section%20300%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCulpable%20homicide%20is%20not%20murder%20if%20it%20is%20committed%20without%20premeditation%20in%20a%20sudden%20fight%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20passion%20upon%20a%20sudden%20quarrel%20and%20without%20the%20offender%20having%20taken%20undue%20advantage%20or%20acted%20in%20a%20cruel%20or%20unusual%20manner.%26quot%3B%20The%20top%20court%20noted%20the%20incident%20of%20April%2019%2C%201984%20started%20with%20a%20fight%20between%20children%20over%20mangoes%20which%20unfortunately%20flared%20up%20when%20the%20adults%20of%20the%20families%20also%20got%20involved%20which%20ultimately%20led%20to%20Vishwanath%20Singh%2C%20the%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20children%2C%20being%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20Singh%20got%20injured%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20at%20Gonda%20by%20bullock%20cart%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead%20and%20a%20post-mortem%20was%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20out%20of%20the%20five%20ante-mortem%20injuries%20recorded%20in%20the%20postmortem%20report%2C%20two%20injuries%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20fatal%20and%20Singh's%20skull%20was%20fractured%20which%20ultimately%20led%20to%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20there%20were%20eyewitnesses%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20particularly%20three%20eyewitnesses%20out%20of%20which%20one%20of%20them%20had%20got%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20put%20to%20a%20lengthy%20cross-examination%20in%20the%20trial%20but%20nothing%20has%20come%20which%20could%20cast%20any%20doubt%20on%20their%20testimony.%20Under%20these%20circumstances%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20death%20is%20homicidal%20is%20not%20in%20question%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20deceased%20died%20due%20to%20the%20injuries%20caused%20to%20him%20by%20the%20lathi%20blows%20inflicted%20by%20the%20appellants%2C%20has%20also%20been%20clearly%20established%20by%20the%20evidence%20placed%20by%20the%20prosecution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20noted%2C%20while%20disposing%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Maheshwari%20said%20the%20convicts%20have%20served%20a%20few%20years%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20case%20but%20were%20granted%20bail%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20appeal%20in%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20currently%20in%20jail%20for%20serving%20the%20remaining%20jail%20term%20after%20their%20life%20sentence%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20high%20court%20on%20December%2021%2C%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722963840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fogmcqm2g_supreme-court-of-india_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchildrens-fight-over-mangoes-sc-reduces-life-term-of-three-to-7-year-jail-after-40-years-6277947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forty%20years%20after%20three%20men%20were%20booked%20for%20murder%20following%20a%20trivial%20fight%20among%20children%20over%20mangoes%20in%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20village%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20come%20to%20their%20rescue%20by%20reducing%20the%20life%20sentence%20to%20a%20seven-year%20jail%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchildrens-fight-over-mangoes-sc-reduces-life-term-of-three-to-7-year-jail-a