members%20and%20supporters%20of%20the%20Lebanese%20armed%20group%20had%20gathered%20to%20watch%20a%20televised%20speech%20by%20its%20leader%20to%20mark%20the%20one-week%20anniversary%20of%20Israel's%20killing%20of%20a%20senior%20military%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20began%2C%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20said%20the%20sonic%20booms%20were%20intended%20to%20provoke%20those%20gathered%20for%20the%20memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20that%20killed%20commander%20Fuad%20Shukr%20was%20the%20second%20time%20Israel%20had%20struck%20the%20southern%20suburbs%20in%2010%20months%20of%20hostilities%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20the%20Israeli%20military%20that%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20parallel%20with%20the%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20launched%20a%20swarm%20of%20attack%20drones%20at%20two%20military%20sites%20near%20Acre%20in%20northern%20Israel%20and%20also%20attacked%20an%20Israeli%20military%20vehicle%20in%20another%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20a%20number%20of%20hostile%20drones%20were%20identified%20crossing%20from%20Lebanon%20and%20one%20was%20intercepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20medical%20officials%20said%20seven%20people%20were%20evacuated%20to%20hospital%2C%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Nahariya%2C%20one%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20an%20initial%20investigation%20indicated%20the%20injuries%20were%20caused%20by%20an%20interceptor%20that%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20the%20target%20and%20hit%20the%20ground%2C%20injuring%20several%20civilians.%26quot%3B%20It%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20still%20under%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20journalists%20saw%20one%20impact%20site%20near%20a%20bus%20stop%20on%20a%20main%20road%20outside%20Nahariya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20sirens%20sounded%20around%20Acre%2C%20but%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20false%20alarm.%20It%20said%20its%20air%20force%20struck%20two%20Hezbollah%20facilities%20in%20south%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFears%20are%20rising%20that%20the%20Middle%20East%20could%20tip%20into%20full-blown%20war%20following%20vows%20by%20Hezbollah%20to%20avenge%20Shukr's%20killing%2C%20and%20by%20Iran%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20assassination%20in%20Tehran%20last%20week%20of%20the%20head%20of%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hezbollah%20source%20told%20Reuters%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20response%20to%20the%20assassination%20of%20commander%20Fuad%20Shukr%20has%20not%20yet%20come%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20four%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20strike%20on%20a%20home%20in%20the%20Lebanese%20town%20of%20Mayfadoun%2C%20nearly%2030%20km%20(19%20miles)%20north%20of%20the%20border%2C%20medics%20and%20a%20security%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722961200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fi0gaa9mo_israel-lebanon_625x300_06_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-aircraft-fly-at-low-altitude-over-beirut-breaking-sound-barrier-6277717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20warplanes%20swooped%20low%20over%20the%20Lebanese%20capital%20Beirut%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20series%20of%20sonic%20booms%20that%20rattled%20windows%20across%20the%20city%20minutes%20before%20the%20head%20of%20Lebanon's%20Hezbollah%20was%20set%20to%20give%20an%20address.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-aircraft-fly-at-low-altitude-over-beirut-breaking-sound-barrier-6277717%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.am