20in%20Delhi%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20which%20will%20be%20a%20strategy%20session%20with%20alliance%20partner%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20meeting%20with%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20other%20leaders%20including%20Sonia%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20is%20due%20tomorrow.%20A%20few%20other%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20meet%20later%20-%20their%20first%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20meeting%20with%20Sena%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20will%20have%20an%20internal%20meet%20tomorrow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20UBT%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%2C%20at%20whose%20house%20Mr%20Thackeray%20and%20his%20son%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20are%20staying%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20in%20Delhi%20so%20the%20discussion%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20want%20to%20bring%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20election%20for%20Maharashtra's%20288%20seats%20is%20due%20in%20October%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20hoping%20for%20a%20major%20comeback%2C%20powered%20by%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20-%20allied%20with%20the%20undivided%20Sena%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20-%20won%2023%20of%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20it%20contested%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20contested%20the%20other%2023%20and%20won%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20just%20nine%20seats.%20Its%20allies%20--%20the%20splinter%20units%20of%20the%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20NCP%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20--%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2019%20seats%20they%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20were%20seen%20as%20the%20voters'%20take%20on%20the%20massive%20political%20tumult%20that%20had%20overtaken%20the%20state%20since%20the%202019%20state%20elections.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20matter%20has%20escalated%2C%20leading%20to%20back-t9o-back%20splits%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20with%20the%20rebel%20factions%20in%20both%20groups%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20president%20Nana%20Patole%20has%20already%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20a%20change%20in%20the%20government%20is%20inevitable%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20tomorrow's%20strategy%20session%20is%20expected%20to%20draw%20up%20a%20roadmap.%20The%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20--%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722955320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmg6p0jn_uddhav-thackeray-1200_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-maharashtra-polls-uddhav-thackerays-huddle-with-congress-6277803%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20leader%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20is%20in%20Delhi%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20which%20will%20be%20a%20strategy%20session%20with%20alliance%20partner%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-maharashtra-polls-uddhav-thackerays-huddle-with-congress-6277803%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20leaders%20laud%20B