C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20presidential%20candidate%20Kamala%20Harris%20selected%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20Walz%20to%20be%20her%20running%20mate%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20choosing%20a%20progressive%20policy%20champion%20and%20a%20plain%20speaker%20from%20America's%20heartland%20to%20help%20win%20over%20rural%2C%20white%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20announced%20the%20selection%20in%20a%20text%20message%20to%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pleased%20to%20share%20that%20I've%20made%20my%20decision%3A%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20Walz%20will%20join%20our%20campaign%20as%20my%20running%20mate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BTim%20is%20a%20battle-tested%20leader%20who%20has%20an%20incredible%20track%20record%20of%20getting%20things%20done%20for%20Minnesota%20families.%20I%20know%20that%20he%20will%20bring%20that%20same%20principled%20leadership%20to%20our%20campaign%2C%20and%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20vice%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20U.S.%20Army%20National%20Guard%20veteran%20and%20former%20teacher%2C%20was%20elected%20to%20a%20Republican-leaning%20district%20in%20the%20U.S.%20House%20of%20Representatives%20in%202006%20and%20served%2012%20years%20before%20being%20elected%20governor%20of%20Minnesota%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20am%20proud%20to%20announce%20that%20I've%20asked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTim_Walz%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Tim_Walz%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20my%20running%20mate.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20a%20governor%2C%20a%20coach%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20and%20a%20veteran%2C%20he's%20delivered%20for%20working%20families%20like%20his.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20great%20to%20have%20him%20on%20the%20team.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%20let's%20get%20to%20work.%20Join%20us%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW4AE2WlMTj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW4AE2WlMTj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kamala%20Harris%20(%40KamalaHarris)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKamalaHarris%2Fstatus%2F1820828396298879294%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20governor%2C%20Walz%20has%20pushed%20a%20progressive%20agenda%20that%20includes%20free%20school%20meals%2C%20goals%20for%20tackling%20climate%20change%2C%20tax%20cuts%20for%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20expanded%20paid%20leave%20for%20Minnesota%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20has%20long%20advocated%20for%20women's%20reproductive%20rights%20but%20also%20displayed%20a%20conservative%20bent%20while%20representing%20a%20rural%20district%20in%20the%20U.S.%20House%2C%20defending%20agricultural%20interests%20and%20backing%20gun%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20immigrants%20from%20Jamaica%20and%20India%2C%20is%20adding%20a%20popular%20Midwestern%20politician%20whose%20home%20state%20votes%20reliably%20for%20Democrats%20in%20presidential%20elections%20but%20is%20close%20to%20Wisconsin%20and%20Michigan%2C%20two%20crucial%20battlegrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20states%20are%20seen%20as%20critical%20in%20deciding%20the%20Nov.%205%20election%2C%20and%20Walz%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20skilled%20at%20connecting%20with%20white%2C%20rural%20voters%20who%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20voted%20broadly%20for%20Republican%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Harris'%20rival%20for%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20chose%20Walz%20over%20Josh%20Shapiro%2C%20the%20popular%20governor%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20who%20had%20been%20seen%20as%20helpful%20to%20delivering%20his%20crucial%20battleground%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%2C%2059%2C%20became%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20standard%20bearer%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%2081%2C%20ended%20his%20reelection%20campaign%20under%20party%20pressure%20last%20month.%20Since%20then%2C%20she%20has%20raised%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20and%20recast%20the%20race%20against%20Trump%20with%20a%20boost%20of%20energy%20from%20her%20party's%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20was%20expected%20to%20appear%20with%20her%20running%20mate%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Philadelphia%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Harris%20campaign%20hopes%20Walz's%20extensive%20National%20Guard%20career%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20successful%20run%20as%20a%20high%20school%20football%20coach%2C%20and%20his%20Dad%20joke%20videos%20will%20attract%20rural%20voters%20who%20are%20not%20yet%20dedicated%20to%20a%20second%20Trump%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20was%20a%20relative%20unknown%20nationally%20until%20the%20Harris%20%26quot%3Bveepstakes%26quot%3B%20heated%20up%2C%20but%20his%20profile%20has%20since%20surged.%20A%20popular%20member%20of%20Congress%2C%20he%20reportedly%20had%20the%20backing%20of%20powerful%20former%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%2C%20who%20was%20instrumental%20in%20persuading%20Biden%20to%20leave%20the%20race.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20and%20Walz%20will%20face%20Trump%20and%20his%20running%20mate%20JD%20Vance%2C%20also%20a%20military%20veteran%20from%20the%20Midwest%2C%20in%20the%20November%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20George%20Floyd%20Factor%20In%20Walz's%20Tenure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz's%20tenure%20as%20governor%20was%20marked%20by%20the%20May%202020%20killing%20of%20George%20Floyd%2C%20a%20Black%20man%2C%20by%20a%20white%20Minneapolis%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20convicted%20of%20murder.%20Walz%20assigned%20the%20state's%20attorney%20general%20to%20lead%20the%20prosecution%20in%20the%20case%2C%20saying%20people%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20believe%20justice%20can%20be%20served.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERev.%20Al%20Sharpton%2C%20founder%20and%20president%20of%20National%20Action%20Network%2C%20said%20Walz%20had%20heard%20calls%20for%20justice%20for%20Floyd%20by%20tapping%20the%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20then%20that%20he%20was%20a%20man%20who%20will%20listen%20and%20do%20what%20is%20right%20by%20those%20he%20represents%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharpton%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20count%20on%20Governor%20Walz%20to%20take%20that%20same%20kind%20of%20open%20approach%20as%20Kamala%20Harris'%20vice%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20campaign%20officials%20and%20surrogates%20quickly%20went%20to%20work%20trying%20to%20define%20Walz%20as%20a%20hardcore%20leftist%20whose%20values%20are%20out%20of%20touch%20with%20most%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20criticized%20his%20handling%20of%20violent%20riots%20in%20Minneapolis%20following%20Floyd's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%20San%20Francisco%20Liberal%20Kamala%20Harris%20wants%20West%20Coast%20wannabe%20Tim%20Walz%20as%20her%20running-mate%20-%20Walz%20has%20spent%20his%20governorship%20trying%20to%20reshape%20Minnesota%20in%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Golden%20State%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20California%2C%20Harris'%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWalz%20On%20The%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20has%20attacked%20Trump%20and%20Vance%20as%20%26quot%3Bweird%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20catchy%20insult%20that%20has%20been%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Harris%20campaign%2C%20social%20media%20and%20Democratic%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20gave%20the%20nascent%20Harris%20campaign%20the%20new%20attack%20line%20in%20a%20late%20July%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20weird%20people%20on%20the%20other%20side%3A%20They%20want%20to%20take%20books%20away.%20They%20want%20to%20be%20in%20your%20exam%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20book%20bans%20and%20women's%20reproductive%20consultations%20with%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20has%20also%20assailed%20claims%20by%20Trump%20and%20Vance%20of%20having%20middle%20class%20credentials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20keep%20talking%20about%20the%20middle%20class.%20A%20robber%20baron%20real%20estate%20guy%20and%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20trying%20to%20tell%20us%20they%20understand%20who%20we%20are%3F%20They%20don't%20know%20who%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Walz%20said%20in%20an%20MSNBC%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20has%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20the%20young%20voters%20Harris%20needs%20to%20reengage.%20David%20Hogg%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20the%20gun%20safety%20group%20March%20for%20Our%20Lives%2C%20described%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20communicator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20is%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20of%20a%20unicorn%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ryan%20Dawkins%2C%20a%20political%20science%20professor%20at%20Minnesota's%20Carleton%20College%20-%20a%20man%20born%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20rural%20Nebraska%20capable%20of%20conveying%20Harris'%20message%20to%20core%20Democratic%20voters%2C%20and%20those%20that%20the%20party%20has%20failed%20to%20reach%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDawkins%20praised%20his%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20rural%20voters.%20It%20is%20a%20group%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20tried%20to%20reach%20with%20infrastructure%20spending%20and%20other%20pragmatic%20policies%2C%20but%20with%20little%20show%20of%20messaging%20success%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202016%20election%2C%20Trump%20won%2059%25%20of%20rural%20voters%3B%20in%202020%20that%20number%20rose%20to%2065%25%20even%20though%20Trump%20lost%20the%20election%2C%20according%20to%20Pew%20Research.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202022%20governor's%20race%2C%20Walz%20won%20with%2052.27%25%20to%20his%20Republican%20opponent's%2044.61%25%2C%20although%20swaths%20of%20rural%20Minnesota%20voted%20for%20the%20opponent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Walz%20has%20supported%20Democratic%20Party%20orthodoxy%20on%20issues%20ranging%20from%20legalized%20abortion%20and%20same-sex%20marriage%20to%20the%20Affordable%20Care%20Act%2C%20known%20as%20Obamacare%2C%20he%20also%20racked%20up%20a%20centrist%20voting%20record%20during%20his%20congressional%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20staunch%20defender%20of%20government%20support%20for%20farmers%20and%20military%20veterans%2C%20as%20well%20as%20gun-owner%20rights%20that%20won%20praise%20from%20the%20National%20Rifle%20Association%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Almanac%20of%20American%20Politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20subsequently%20registered%20a%20failing%20grade%20with%20the%20NRA%20after%20supporting%20gun-control%20measures%20during%20his%20first%20campaign%20for%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz's%20shift%20from%20a%20centrist%20representing%20a%20single%20rural%20district%20in%20Congress%20to%20a%20more%20progressive%20politician%20as%20governor%20may%20have%20been%20in%20response%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20voters%20in%20major%20cities%20like%20Minneapolis-St.%20Paul.%20But%20it%20leaves%20him%20open%20to%20Republican%20attacks%2C%20Dawkins%20said%20in%20a%20telephone%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20reinforcing%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20fears%20people%20have%20of%20Kamala%20Harris%20being%20a%20San%20Francisco%20liberal%2C%26quot%3B%20Dawkins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20has%20a%20ready%20counter-attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20monster.%20Kids%20are%20eating%20and%20having%20full%20bellies%2C%20so%20they%20can%20go%20learn%20and%20women%20are%20making%20their%20own%20healthcare%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20Walz%20said%20in%20a%20July%20CNN%20interview.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20that's%20where%20they%20want%20to%20label%20me%2C%20I'm%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20take%20the%20label.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20state's%20top%20executive%2C%20Walz%20mandated%20the%20use%20of%20face%20coverings%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2