ot%3BKicked%2C%20Crushed%20In%20Own%20Country%26quot%3B%3A%20Bajrang%20On%20Vinesh%20After%20Olympics%20Heroics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20made%20the%20headlines%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20two%20memorable%20wins%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20which%20saw%20the%20champion%20wrestler%20go%20close%20to%20a%20first%20medal%20at%20the%20Games.%20It%20was%20sort%20of%20full%20circle%20for%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20was%20a%20leading%20face%20in%20the%20protests%20that%20happened%20last%20year%20against%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%20The%20starting%20game%20at%20the%20Paris%20Games%20was%20historic%20for%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20as%20she%20defeated%20the%20top%20seed%20and%20Tokyo%202020%20champion%20Yui%20Susaki%20of%20Japan%20in%20the%20women's%2050kg%20freestyle%20round%20of%2016%20match%20on%20Tuesday.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmedals-tally%5C%22%3EOlympics%202024%20Medals%20Tally%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tokyo%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20and%20four-time%20world%20champion%20Susaki%20had%20not%20lost%20any%20of%20her%2082%20bouts%20in%20her%20international%20career%20but%20the%20Japanese%20top%20seed%20hardly%20had%20an%20idea%20as%20to%20what%20was%20about%20to%20hit%20her%20in%20the%20opener%20which%20she%20lost%202-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Vinesh%20quelled%20the%20challenge%20of%20former%20European%20champion%20and%202018%20world%20championship%20bronze-medallist%20Livach%207-5%20in%20the%20quarterfinal.%20Vinesh's%20semi-final%20will%20happen%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20endured%20two%20Olympic%20heart-breaks%2C%20the%20feisty%2029-year-old%2C%20is%20now%20only%20one%20win%20away%20from%20ensuring%20her%20maiden%20Olympic%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20along%20with%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20of%20the%20country%20who%20led%2