oration%20and%20plants%2C%20she%20started%20growing%20them.%20She%20was%20a%20natural%20at%20it%20and%20her%20home%20was%20soon%20filled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20friends%20started%20asking%20me%20for%20ways%20to%20grow%20and%20take%20care%20of%20plants.%20Since%20this%20was%20a%20much%20asked%20question%2C%20I%20started%20sharing%20tips%20on%20home%20decor%20and%20growing%20indoor%20plants%20on%20Instagram%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aprajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20compost%20for%20plants%20and%20tending%20to%20them%20also%20led%20her%20into%20the%20world%20of%20sustainability.%20Back%20home%20in%20Himachal%2C%20climate%20change%20had%20adversely%20impacted%20their%20produce%20as%20well.%20She%20started%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20combat%20it%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20shift%20to%20natural%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20returned%20home%20in%20July%202021%2C%20the%20harvest%20season%2C%20she%20found%20that%20her%20parents%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20for%20their%20produce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20to%20sell%20our%20apples.%20Later%2C%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eopened%20up%20in%20Himachal.%20Due%20to%20middlemen%2C%20no%20farmer%20ever%20gets%20the%20full%20value%20that%20he%20deserves.%20After%20my%20daughter%20started%20selling%20it%20online%2C%20things%20have%20completely%20changed.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20market%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Bansal%2C%20who%20has%20been%20farming%20since%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPained%20by%20what%20she%20saw%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20help%20her%20father%20get%20the%20right%20price.%20She%20asked%20her%20Instagram%20community%20(which%20was%20then%20about%2010%2C000)%20if%20they%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20buy%20their%20apples%2C%20freshly%20plucked%20from%20the%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aprajita%20Bansal%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAprajita%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%20grown%20in%20her%20family%20orchard.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20her%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%20the%20response%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive.%20She%20hosted%20a%20sale%20online%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20%E2%80%98Him2Home%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20rebranded%20to%20Phal%20Phool%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20were%20overjoyed%20and%20had%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20they%20were%20getting%20what%20they%20deserved%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20she%20found%20was%20that%20people%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20different%20varieties%20and%20quality%20of%20apples%20that%20were%20sold%20in%20cities.%20Farmers%20like%20her%20father%2C%20she%20says%2C%20struggle%20to%20even%20get%2030-40%20percent%20of%20the%20price%20their%20products%20are%20sold%20for%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20apples%20you%20find%20in%20the%20market%20are%20often%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20stock%20stored%20in%20cold%20storage%20or%20imported%20from%20other%20countries%20and%20stored%20similarly%20for%20extended%20periods.%20The%20apple%20season%20in%20Himachal%20has%20just%20begun%2C%20and%20many%20middlemen%20are%20attempting%20to%20clear%20their%20old%20stock%2C%E2%80%9D%20warns%20Aprajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20she%20has%20sold%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297977%2Fex-banker-turns-barren-land-into-apple-orchard-in-himachal-kalasan-nursery-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreshly%20harvested%20apples%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20her%20farm%20in%20July%20to%20customers%20across%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20completely%20sold%20out%20this%20year%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20happily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%E2%80%99s%20been%20able%20to%20give%20her%20father%20three%20times%20the%20profit%20that%20he%20used%20to%20receive%20when%20he%20sold%20them%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandi%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECombating%20climate%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20this%20third%20generation%20farmer%20did%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20was%20move%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%2C%20natural%20way%20of%20farming.%20Thanks%20to%20work-from-home%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20assist%20her%20parents%20on%20the%20orchard%20while%20continuing%20her%20full-time%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9sNhIoSUXh%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2F