0was%20forced%20to%20sell%2015-acre%20of%20his%20farmland%20%E2%80%94%20his%20only%20treasure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20take%20the%20decision%20of%20selling%20my%20farmland.%20For%20any%20farmer%2C%20his%20land%20is%20his%20only%20treasure.%20I%20was%20so%20depressed%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20out%20of%20my%20home%20for%20a%20year%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20weddings%20or%20local%20events%20for%20four%20years.%20I%20would%20make%20excuses%20to%20avoid%20speaking%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20some%20time%20had%20passed%2C%20he%20recollected%20a%20trade%20fair%20which%20he%20attended%20in%20Delhi%20in%201993%2C%20showcasing%20the%20advantages%20of%20soybean%20cultivation%20and%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20newfound%20determination%2C%20he%20underwent%20training%20in%20preparing%20soy%20milk%20and%20soy%20paneer%20from%20the%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Agricultural%20Engineering%20(CIAE)%2C%20Bhopal%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%2C%20he%20established%20a%20small%20one-room%20factory%20to%20produce%20soy%20milk%20and%20tofu.%20Without%20any%20other%20modes%20of%20marketing%20the%20products%2C%20he%20started%20giving%20them%20as%20samples%20to%20customers%20that%20came%20to%20his%20grocery%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20challenging%20to%20market%20this%20product%20in%20a%20place%20where%20people%20preferred%20cow%20and%20buffalo%20milk.%20So%2C%20even%20though%20they%20liked%20its%20taste%2C%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20purchase%20it.%20My%20family%20also%20questioned%20me%20why%20I%20was%20manufacturing%20it%20when%20I%20had%20no%20customers.%20But%20I%20believed%20in%20myself%20that%20one%20day%2C%20this%20work%20would%20scale%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20make%20the%20first%20sale%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20PAU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%