n%20processing%20plant.%20Depending%20on%20the%20demand%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20freshly%20prepares%20up%20to%20700%20litres%20of%20milk%20and%20four%20quintals%20of%20tofu%20daily.%20This%20earns%20him%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2010-12%20lakh%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBachchattar%20has%20trained%20his%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Karanveer%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20the%20processing%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaranveer%2C%20who%20has%20been%20helping%20him%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20not%20only%20taught%20me%20the%20processing%20work%20but%20also%20the%20learnings%20of%20his%20life.%20We%20should%20not%20give%20up%20on%20hard%20work%20irrespective%20of%20ups%20and%20downs.%20Although%20he%20has%20trained%20me%2C%20he%20still%20goes%20to%20work%20every%20day%20despite%20his%20age.%20It%E2%80%99s%20truly%20inspirational.%20Seeing%20him%2C%20I%20wonder%20why%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20as%20active%20as%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20he%20has%20received%20numerous%20awards%20including%20the%20State%20Award%20in%202003%20and%20the%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20National%20Award%20in%202004.%20He%20was%20also%20facilitated%20with%20soil%20beverage%20of%20the%20year%202023%20award%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20Indian%20soy%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bachchattar%20says%2C%20he%20reinvested%20his%20earnings%20into%20purchasing%20the%20land%20he%20had%20previously%20sold%2C%20reclaiming%20the%20ownership%20of%20seven%20out%20of%20the%2015%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20to%20get%20the%20entire%20land%20that%20I%20had%20to%20sell%20in%20dire%20times.%20I%20started%20soybean%20processing%20at%20a%20time%20in%20Punjab%20when%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20about%20soy%20milk%20or%20tofu.%20But%20today%2C%20I%20have%20not%20only%20established%20myself%20again%20to%20walk%20with%20dignity%20in%20society%20but%20also%20build%20a%20good%20future%20for%20my%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%20journey%20since%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pau.edu%2Findex.php%3F_act%3DmanageEvent%26DO%3DviewEventDetail%26intID%3D7767%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESangrur%20Based%20Soybean%20Processor%20S.%20Bachittar%20Singh%20Garcha%20Awareded%20with%20SFPWA%E2%80%99s%20Prestigious%20Award-%20Soy%20Beverage%20of%20the%20Year%202023%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Punjab%20Agricultural%20University%20on%204%20July%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Bachchattar%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722849924000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPunjab-1-1722848961.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bachchattar%20Singh%20Garcha%20of%20Deh%20Kalan%20village%2C%20Punjab%20turned%20to%20soybean%20cultivation%20and%20processing%20after%20incurring%20huge%20losses%20in%20potato%20farming.%20He%20now%20runs%20an%20automatic%20plant%20to%20process%20soybean%20into%20milk%20and%20tofu%2C%20clocking%20in%20an%20annual%20sale%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2048%20lakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manika%20Batra%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Table%20Tennis%20Queen%20at%20Olympics%20Who%20Was%20Told%20%E2%80%98She%E2%80%99s%20Wasting%20Time%20With%20Sports%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20hearts%20of%20countless%20Indians%20swelled%20with%20pride%20as%20Manika%20Batra%20made%20history%20on%2029%20July%2C%202024%2C%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20table%20tennis%20player%20to%20reach%20the%20round%20of%2016%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20singles%20competition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20victory%20came%20after%20a%204-0%20thrashing%20of%20Prithika%20Pavade%20of%20France.%20What%20adds%20to%20the%20thrill%20is%20that%20Manika%20is%20currently%20ranked%2028th%20in%20the%20world%2C%2010%20places%20lower%20than%20Pavade.%20She%20secured%20her%20victory%20with%20game%20scores%20of%2011-9%2C%2011-6%2C%2011-9%2C%20and%2011-7%20against%20her%20French%20opponent%20of%20Indian%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20securing%20the%20title%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20table%20tennis%20player%20to%20reach%20Olympics%20pre-quarterfinals%2C%20Manika%20reflected%20through%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram%2C%20%E2%80%9CReaching%20the%20pre-quarterfinals%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Singles%20in%20Olympics%20has%20been%20a%20milestone%2C%20but%20I%20always%20want%20more.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20have%20a%20dream%2C%20an%20aim%2C%20I%20will%20keep%20doing%20my%20best.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20hails%20from%20Delhi%20and%20is%20the%20youngest%20of%20three%20siblings.%20At%20the%20young%20age%20of%20four%2C%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20sport%20by%20her%20sister%2C%20Aanchal%2C%20and%20brother%20Sahil%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20also%20played%20table%20tennis.%20It%20became%20clear%20that%20she%20was%20destined%20for%20greatness%20when%20she%20won%20a%20state-level%20under-8%20tournament%2C%20prompting%20her%20to%20train%20under%20coach%20Sandeep%20Gupta%20at%20Hans%20Raj%20Model%20School.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManika%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20fame%20began%20with%20a%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%20under-21%20category%20at%20the%202011%20Chile%20Open.%20She%20also%20achieved%20quarterfinal%20finishes%20while%20representing%20India%20at%20the%202014%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20Glasgow%20and%20the%202014%20Asian%20Games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20breakthrough%20arrived%20at%20the%202015%20Commonwealth%20Table%20Tennis%20Championships%2C%20where%20s