alth%20Table%20Tennis%20Championships.%20Her%20achievement%20of%20becoming%20the%20first%20paddler%20to%20reach%20round%20of%2016%20surpasses%20her%20previous%20record%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20where%20she%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20women%E2%80%99s%20table%20tennis%20player%20to%20reach%20the%20round%20of%2032%20in%20singles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20Tokyo%20Games%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293449%2Fsharath-kamal-table-tennis-player-at-men-single-commonwealth-games-father-dream%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAchanta%20Sharath%20Kamal%20had%20also%20reached%20the%20round%20of%2032%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20singles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20she%20won%20the%20WTT%20Contender%20Budapest%20mixed%20doubles%20and%20the%20WTT%20Contender%20Lasko%20women%E2%80%99s%20doubles.%20She%20competed%20in%20the%20inaugural%20WTT%20Grand%20Smash%20event%20in%20Singapore%20in%202022%20and%20achieved%20a%20career-high%20ranking%20of%20world%20number%20four%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20doubles%20with%20Archana%20Girish%20Kamath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManika%20aspires%20to%20do%20for%20table%20tennis%20in%20India%20what%20PV%20Sindhu%20and%20Saina%20Nehwal%20did%20for%20badminton%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20table%20tennis%2C%20badminton%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20famous%20(in%20India)%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fathletes%2Fmanika-batra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManika%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20amount%20of%20recognition%20they%20have%20got%20for%20the%20sport%2C%20I%20would%20also%20like%20to%20take%20table%20tennis%20to%20greater%20heights%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhilst%20table%20tennis%20was%20her%20first%20love%2C%20Manika%20turned%20down%20modelling%20offers%20in%20her%20teens%20to%20concentrate%20on%20the%20sport.%2